      "content": "```python\ndef calculate_final_price(order):\n    subtotal = order['subtotal']\n    region = order['region']\n    discount_code = order.get('discount_code')\n    if region == 'UK' and discount_code == 'SAVE10':\n        subtotal = subtotal * 0.9\n    elif region == 'EU' and discount_code == 'EU_PROMO':\n        subtotal = subtotal * 0.95\n    if region == 'UK':\n        subtotal *= 1.2\n    elif region == 'EU':\n        subtotal *= 1.15\n    return subtotal\n```\nThis function applies the correct discount and VAT for each region and discount code, matching the expected outputs in your tests.",
